    <!-- ==========================================
         INTRO — Why We Exist
         ========================================== -->
    <section class="section" id="intro">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-label">Why We Exist</span>
          <h2>Because identity doesn't disappear &mdash; it needs to be held.</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content-width">
          <p class="lead">
            Memory loss changes everything &mdash; the rhythms of a household, the ease of
            conversation, the quiet certainties we once took for granted. But it does not erase
            who someone is. Beneath the shifting surface, there is still a whole person with a
            lifetime of meaning, humor, warmth, and worth.
          </p>
          <p class="lead">
            The Still Me Project provides thoughtful frameworks, practical tools, and genuine
            human connection so that families and caregivers can continue to honor the whole
            person &mdash; not just the diagnosis.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


